Flora Finch https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flora_Finch 0 Flora Finch (17 June 1867 – 4 January 1940) was an English-born vaudevillian, stage and film actress who starred in over 300 silent films, including over 200 for the Vitagraph Studios film company.
